# Typography Rules (Strict Usage)

- UI elements (buttons, tabs, labels, interface controls) must use:
  - `IBM Plex Sans Arabic` + `IBM Plex Sans`
- Long Arabic content (Azkar, Quran, Dua, long passages) must use:
  - `Noto Naskh Arabic`
- Always apply the correct font explicitly (do not rely on inherited defaults).
- Never mix fonts incorrectly within the same text role.

# Implementation Guidance

- Prefer dedicated font utilities/classes such as `font-ui` and `font-content`.
- If these utilities do not exist yet, define them during the “define design tokens” stage, then use them consistently.
- Use RTL-aware layout/alignment as required by the UI reference.

